This paper deals with a communication system, specifically a broadcast channel, and focuses on the use of channel state information (CSI) to improve the transmission. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.COMM (Communications), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
